
			HUMAN ASPECT
		User posibility
- Modification des informations personel. --> formulaire -> JS: - hashage then ask + cmp && chg
- Prendre des photo via WebCam. --> video/canvas/button -> JS:
															- when button press take picture
															- ask for modif
																- TRUE = go to modification frame / FLASE = go next
																	- proposing several pictures for mount the new one.
																	- go next after validating
															- ask for saving picture
																- TRUE = save it on db and put it in galery / FALSE = return before
- Voir toute la galerie existente --> Sort -> PHP:
												- Several proposal type of sort
												- SELECT from db with the sort asked
												- display result (JS)?
												- button report/like
												- input comment
												- destroy comment from C_user

		Visitor posibility
- Creation de comptes --> formulaire -> JS: - hashage then send to (PHP?/server?)
- Connection et Deconnection! --> formulaire -> JS: - hashage then ask to server for cmp
- Voir la galerie visieur --> display -> PHP:
											- SELECT VisGal db
											- display db (JS)?

		Admin part
- Gestion de comptes utilisateur --> formulaire -> JS:
													- Invite user to be moderator
													- Send a warning to user
													- See report list
													- Ban account
- Gestion de galery --> clickable -> JS:
										- Destroy ALL user comment
										- Destroy pictures

		Moderator posibility
- Gestion de galery et commentaire --> clickable -> JS:
														- Destroy ALL user comment
														- Ask for a destruct picture
														- Ban account for limited time


			DATABASE ASPECT
		User database
TABLE --> Ulogs
			| login (string alpha/digit/ALPHA ONLY NO CONDITION) | password (string alpha/digit/ALPHA ONLY REQUIRE ALL) | id (NUMBER > 0) |
TABLE --> Uintel
			| id (NUMBER > 0) | mail (hexa) | celltel (string digit ONLY) |
TABLE --> Upict
			| id (NUMBER > 0) | picture (ARRAY(Pname => pict path)) |

		Visitor database
TABLE -->Vpict
			| picture (Array(Pname => pict path)) |
